title: Variance of linear combinations of random variables
---
body:

## Problem

Let

$$
f\_{X,Y}(x,y) = 
\begin{cases}
c(x+y) & 0 \leq x \leq 1, 0 \leq y \leq 2 \\\
0 & \text{otherwise}
\end{cases}
$$

Where $c$ is a constant. Find $V(2X - 3Y + 8)$.

